    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>GAMEPLAY:</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take control of PizzaBoy, a nimble pizza delivery guy equipped with an air-dash that allows him to bounce off walls. This can be used to reach greater heights and distances than the standard run and jump. PizzaBoy must navigate dangerous environments to deliver pizzas to hungry monsters. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2238400/extras/9939271f429dd244d660d29e151f986a.poster.avif?t=1772056336\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2238400/extras/9939271f429dd244d660d29e151f986a.webm?t=1772056336\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2238400/extras/9939271f429dd244d660d29e151f986a.mp4?t=1772056336\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pizzaboy must make it to the end of the level to deliver the pizza, but don't expect it to be too simple, as each area is full of pizza-hungry monsters. Don't get too close, or they might just steal a slice! The customer won't be happy with a half-eaten pizza.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2238400/extras/686c50c335866e8e8b25fe7b97bded3f.poster.avif?t=1772056336\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2238400/extras/686c50c335866e8e8b25fe7b97bded3f.webm?t=1772056336\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2238400/extras/686c50c335866e8e8b25fe7b97bded3f.mp4?t=1772056336\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The path to the customer won't always be straightforward either. Every level is a metroidvania style map with many secrets, collectables, and areas to explore. Alongside delivering pizzas, PizzaBoy may find opportunities to recover his lost memories and discover the dark secrets of the company he works for. The player's choice in how they tackle the level will determine the ending of each chapter and ultimately the end of the game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If the customer is satisfied with your performance, you might just get a 5-star review.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2238400/extras/5f266206116df2354cc299cd83c94d1f.poster.avif?t=1772056336\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2238400/extras/5f266206116df2354cc299cd83c94d1f.webm?t=1772056336\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2238400/extras/5f266206116df2354cc299cd83c94d1f.mp4?t=1772056336\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>CHARACTERS:</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2238400/extras/bc7e9d8749ab0ff23d1a899467dcfb4b.avif?t=1772056336\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2238400/extras_big/bc7e9d8749ab0ff23d1a899467dcfb4b.avif?t=1772056336 width=800 height=267 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >PizzaBoy is a loyal employee of 'Pizza Dawg's Pizza' who has recently been promoted to a more dangerous job (that pays an extra 60 cents an hour).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Not much is known about his identity, as he seems to have lost all memories of his past.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >While delivering pizza, he falls in love with a vampire.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2238400/extras/6251ffd1ec13bbebdade74ccb5ec0ece.avif?t=1772056336\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2238400/extras_big/6251ffd1ec13bbebdade74ccb5ec0ece.avif?t=1772056336 width=800 height=267 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >VampireGirl is one of the last surviving vampires on earth. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For unknown reasons, she has a burning hatred for pizza delivery guys. In her free time, she orders pizzas just to kill them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >However, she makes an exception for one...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2238400/extras/adae7c175dce4b47517e56dfa5f4e48b.avif?t=1772056336\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2238400/extras_big/adae7c175dce4b47517e56dfa5f4e48b.avif?t=1772056336 width=800 height=267 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pepperoni Dog.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>STORY:</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In a world where humans and monsters have been in conflict for centuries, PizzaDawg's Pizza is trying to spread the word of peace through the most beautiful delicacy ever created (pizza). Over the past 20 years, PizzaDawg's has been successfully delivering pizzas to monsters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2238400/extras/403d30fc9a8ffbbbfd0502409d8ef23c.gif?t=1772056336\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2238400/extras/403d30fc9a8ffbbbfd0502409d8ef23c.poster.avif?t=1772056336\" class=\"bb_img\" /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Our protagonist, PizzaBoy, is one of the many staff members unfortunate enough to be promoted to monster deliveries. After he gets promoted, life gets a whole lot whackier. While delivering pizzas, he finds himself learning more about the company he works for and even about himself. There are many whacky characters to be found in the world of PizzaBoy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2238400/extras/b3289232c5de1a0c77f2d339a55c0085.gif?t=1772056336\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2238400/extras/b3289232c5de1a0c77f2d339a55c0085.poster.avif?t=1772056336\" class=\"bb_img\" /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game's ending is determined by the player's choice to search for the truth or remain ignorant of the companies' dark secrets.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2238400/extras/e6d1c85120ea3289ecebce3c51734d12.poster.avif?t=1772056336\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2238400/extras/e6d1c85120ea3289ecebce3c51734d12.webm?t=1772056336\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2238400/extras/e6d1c85120ea3289ecebce3c51734d12.mp4?t=1772056336\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
